// LOCALHOST
// =======================

### Root (LOCAL)
GET http://localhost:8080/

### All contacts (LOCAL)
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts

### Create contact (LOCAL) -> expects 201 + { "id": "..." }
POST http://localhost:8080/contacts HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ivan",
  "lastName": "Ribeiro",
  "email": "ivan@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Blue",
  "birthday": "1996-01-01"
}

### Get contact by id (LOCAL)
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts/PASTE_ID_HERE

### Update contact (LOCAL) -> expects 204
PUT http://localhost:8080/contacts/PASTE_ID_HERE HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ivan",
  "lastName": "Ribeiro",
  "email": "ivan.updated@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Green",
  "birthday": "1996-01-01"
}

### Delete contact (LOCAL) -> expects 200
DELETE http://localhost:8080/contacts/PASTE_ID_HERE HTTP/1.1



